John Mitchum https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Mitchum 0 John Mitchum (September 6, 1919 – November 29, 2001) was an American actor from the 1940s to the 1970s in film and television. Early in his career, he was credited as Jack Mitchum. John_Mitchum ( September_6_,_1919 – November_29_,_2001 ) was an_American_actor from the_1940s to the_1970s in film_and_television .
